article_title: The Supreme Court Has Made Obamacare The Defining Issue Of 2016

article_metadata.author: Sally Pipes

og.description: Obamacare's foes should capitalize on the law's ongoing unraveling by coalescing around a replacement plan to put in place the day the president leaves office in 2017. Rep. Tom Price's Empowering Patients First Act represents a good start.
